metadata.name: footsteps a stop, a step
metadata.description:
shrill voice: "Governor, the Ming family big Miss arrived."



Ming LAN if forbear not to see some of that mangled human body, forward salute -



"If Minglan, the eldest eldest daughter of the Ming family, has seen the thousand-year-old father."



On the blood-stained snow, a tall figure in scarlet flying fish suit, like a bright and rampant fire.



The man pulled out the long, blood-covered knife, slowly rubbed it against the corpse's clothes, and turned to look at her.
